              "value": "{\"name\": \"Kagiso Mokoena\", \"email\": \"kagiso@fourwaysfitness.co.za\", \"company\": \"Fourways Fitness\", \"phone\": \"+27 72 555 0199\", \"source\": \"website-form\", \"message\": \"Hi Ian, saw your LinkedIn post about AI automation. We're a 4-studio gym running classes across Joburg, currently drowning in admin — member follow-ups, class bookings, WhatsApp enquiries. Would love a demo of what's possible. Any chance of a call this week?\"}"
            },
